nge_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p id=\"Summary\"></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Retorna um vetor de objetos com todos os elementos filhos&nbsp;que possuem&nbsp;o nome da&nbsp;classe dada. &nbsp;Quando invocado no objeto&nbsp;<em>document</em>, o documento&nbsp;é examinado por completo, incluindo o nó raiz.&nbsp;Você também pode invocar&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/getElementsByClassName\" title=\"getElementsByClassName()\"><code>getElementsByClassName()</code></a> em&nbsp;qualquer elemento; isso retornaria somente elementos&nbsp;que são descendentes do nó raiz especificado&nbsp;com o nome da classe.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>var elementos</var> = document.getElementsByClassName(<em>nomes</em>); // ou:\n<var>var elementos</var> = rootElement.getElementsByClassName(<em>nomes</em>);</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><var>elementos</var>&nbsp;é uma lista viva&nbsp;do <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;elementos encontrados.</li>\n <li><var>nomes</var>&nbsp;é um texto que representa uma&nbsp;lista dos&nbsp;nomes das classes que&nbsp;são separados por espaço em branco.</li>\n <li>getElementsByClassName pode ser invocado&nbsp;por qualquer elemento, não somente pelo nó raiz&nbsp;<em>document. </em>O elemento no qual ele é chamado será usado como a raiz para a&nbsp;busca<em>.</em></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Retorna&nbsp;todos os elementos que possuem a classe&nbsp;'teste'</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByClassName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'teste'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Retorna todos os elementos que possuem as classes 'vermelho' e 'teste'</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByClassName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'vermelho teste'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Retorna todos os elementos que possuem a&nbsp;classe 'teste' dentro do elemento que possui o ID 'principal'</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'principal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByClassName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'teste'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Nós podemos também usar os métodos do&nbsp;Array.prototype em qualquer dos elementos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a> passando o&nbsp;<var>HTMLCollection</var>&nbsp;como valor deste método. Aqui&nbsp;podemos encontrar&nbsp;todos os elementos do tipo <em>div</em>&nbsp;que possuem a classe&nbsp;'teste':</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> elementosTeste <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByClassName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'teste'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> divsTeste <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elementosTeste<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">elementoTeste</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> elementoTeste<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'DIV'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Características</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>3.0</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Características</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/domcore/raw-file/tip/Overview.html#dom-document-getelementsbyclassname\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><span class=\"external\">W3C: getElementsByClassName</span></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"examples"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Retorna um vetor de objetos com todos os elementos filhos que possuem o nome da classe dada.  Quando invocado no objeto document, o documento é examinado por completo, incluindo o nó raiz. Você também pode invocar getElementsByClassName() em qualquer elemento; isso retornaria somente elementos que são descendentes do nó raiz especificado com o nome da classe.","popularity":0.0024,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.getElementsByClassName","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/document/getelementsbyclassname","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/document/getelementsbyclassname/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/getElementsByClassName","title":"Document.getElementsByClassName()"}],"pageTitle":"Document.getElementsByClassName() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}